LTT Hiring Madison is the great news that I needed during this lockdown. She killed it during her ROG Rig Reboot, and it clearly wasn't a fluke. Glad to see the team diversifying up the hosts a bit more! Also, Fry's shutting down definitely isn't a shocker, but it does seem weird that they're doing it NOW of all times, when we're on the cusp of getting a vaccine and the stores opening back up. I mean, they sent me an email 2 days ago for Pete's sake! 

Huh, anyway, now we need to get a Scrapyard Wars with Anthony & Madison vs Wendell and Krista (of Level 1 Techs). Make it happen!

snippet.textDisplay:
Super glad to see Madison on the team! That ROG Reboot episode has probably been the most fun I had watching an LMG video in a while and was really hoping for her to get on board, congrats girl :)

That aside I can't wait to see this "new Windows 10". I like the OS but I was hoping for a refresh for a while now, and I really have my fingers crossed to NOT see Windows 7/8 menus anymore, not even in the installer that still retains the partinioning menus from Win 7.

Hope the update is coming soon and it finally gets rid of everything "old Windows", plus it'd be awesome if they finally made the new Terminal from the Windows Store the default one!
snippet.textOriginal:
Super glad to see Madison on the team! That ROG Reboot episode has probably been the most fun I had watching an LMG video in a while and was really hoping for her to get on board, congrats girl :)

Hope the update is coming soon and it finally gets rid of everything "old Windows", plus it'd be awesome if they finally made the new Terminal from the Windows Store the default one!
